[
    {
        "text": "When you die, you appear in a cinema with a number of other people who look like you.",
        "source": "api",
        "start_time": 0.0,
        "end_time": 0.0,
        "start_progress": 0.0,
        "end_progress": 0.0438871473354232
    },
    {
        "text": "You find out that they are your previous reincarnations, and soon you all begin watching your next life on the big screen.",
        "source": "api",
        "start_time": 0.0,
        "end_time": 0.0,
        "start_progress": 0.044409613375130615,
        "end_progress": 0.10815047021943573
    },
    {
        "text": "On the screen I see myself as a doctor who works in remote areas to save lives.",
        "source": "user",
        "start_time": 0.0,
        "end_time": 69.0,
        "start_progress": 0.10867293625914315,
        "end_progress": 0.1509926854754441
    },
    {
        "text": "One day I am called to a village to treat a patient.",
        "source": "user",
        "start_time": 69.0,
        "end_time": 81.0,
        "start_progress": 0.15151515151515152,
        "end_progress": 0.1786833855799373
    },
    {
        "text": "The patient is very sick and needs medicine.",
        "source": "user",
        "start_time": 81.0,
        "end_time": 106.0,
        "start_progress": 0.17920585161964472,
        "end_progress": 0.20219435736677116
    },
    {
        "text": "I have no medicine with me, but I try to make the patient comfortable and wait for him to get well.",
        "source": "user",
        "start_time": 106.0,
        "end_time": 118.0,
        "start_progress": 0.2027168234064786,
        "end_progress": 0.25444096133751304
    },
    {
        "text": "The next day I went to a different village to find the right medicine for the sick patient.",
        "source": "user",
        "start_time": 118.0,
        "end_time": 159.0,
        "start_progress": 0.2549634273772205,
        "end_progress": 0.30250783699059564
    },
    {
        "text": "I leave the patient behind and continue my journey.",
        "source": "user",
        "start_time": 159.0,
        "end_time": 180.0,
        "start_progress": 0.30303030303030304,
        "end_progress": 0.3296760710553814
    },
    {
        "text": "I found the medicine but it was very expensive.",
        "source": "user",
        "start_time": 180.0,
        "end_time": 196.0,
        "start_progress": 0.33019853709508884,
        "end_progress": 0.3547544409613375
    },
    {
        "text": "I was sad, thinking that the patient will not be able to afford it.",
        "source": "user",
        "start_time": 196.0,
        "end_time": 208.0,
        "start_progress": 0.3552769070010449,
        "end_progress": 0.390282131661442
    },
    {
        "text": "So I used my own money to pay for the medicine to save the man.",
        "source": "user",
        "start_time": 208.0,
        "end_time": 225.0,
        "start_progress": 0.39080459770114945,
        "end_progress": 0.42371995820271685
    },
    {
        "text": "I returned to the village and gave the medicine to the patient.",
        "source": "user",
        "start_time": 225.0,
        "end_time": 234.0,
        "start_progress": 0.42424242424242425,
        "end_progress": 0.45715778474399166
    },
    {
        "text": "After one day the man started regaining his health.",
        "source": "user",
        "start_time": 234.0,
        "end_time": 264.0,
        "start_progress": 0.45768025078369906,
        "end_progress": 0.4843260188087774
    },
    {
        "text": "The patient was very thankful and promised to pay me back.",
        "source": "user",
        "start_time": 264.0,
        "end_time": 276.0,
        "start_progress": 0.48484848484848486,
        "end_progress": 0.5151515151515151
    },
    {
        "text": "I told him it was not necessary since I knew it would be very hard for him to pay me.",
        "source": "user",
        "start_time": 276.0,
        "end_time": 301.0,
        "start_progress": 0.5156739811912225,
        "end_progress": 0.5600835945663531
    },
    {
        "text": "I left the village and continued on with my journey.",
        "source": "user",
        "start_time": 301.0,
        "end_time": 319.0,
        "start_progress": 0.5606060606060606,
        "end_progress": 0.5877742946708464
    },
    {
        "text": "The next day I was called to another village for work.",
        "source": "user",
        "start_time": 319.0,
        "end_time": 351.0,
        "start_progress": 0.5882967607105538,
        "end_progress": 0.6165099268547545
    },
    {
        "text": "This time it was a sick woman who needed medicine.",
        "source": "user",
        "start_time": 351.0,
        "end_time": 369.0,
        "start_progress": 0.6170323928944619,
        "end_progress": 0.6431556948798328
    },
    {
        "text": "She had been sick for a whole week.",
        "source": "user",
        "start_time": 369.0,
        "end_time": 378.0,
        "start_progress": 0.6436781609195402,
        "end_progress": 0.6619644723092999
    },
    {
        "text": "I was still thinking about the patient from the previous day.",
        "source": "user",
        "start_time": 378.0,
        "end_time": 388.0,
        "start_progress": 0.6624869383490073,
        "end_progress": 0.6943573667711599
    },
    {
        "text": "\"What if she also can't afford medicine?\", I wondered.",
        "source": "user",
        "start_time": 388.0,
        "end_time": 423.0,
        "start_progress": 0.6948798328108673,
        "end_progress": 0.723092998955068
    },
    {
        "text": "But I decided to treat the woman anyway.",
        "source": "user",
        "start_time": 423.0,
        "end_time": 437.0,
        "start_progress": 0.7236154649947754,
        "end_progress": 0.7445141065830722
    },
    {
        "text": "I treated her for a few days, and the woman started feeling better.",
        "source": "api",
        "start_time": 437.0,
        "end_time": 450.0,
        "start_progress": 0.7450365726227796,
        "end_progress": 0.7800417972831766
    },
    {
        "text": "She paid me for the medicine.",
        "source": "user",
        "start_time": 450.0,
        "end_time": 469.0,
        "start_progress": 0.780564263322884,
        "end_progress": 0.7957157784743991
    },
    {
        "text": "As it turns out she was very wealthy and could afford the medicine.",
        "source": "user",
        "start_time": 469.0,
        "end_time": 491.0,
        "start_progress": 0.7962382445141066,
        "end_progress": 0.8312434691745036
    },
    {
        "text": "\"I heard what you did,\" she said, referring to paying for the other patient's medicine.",
        "source": "user",
        "start_time": 491.0,
        "end_time": 522.0,
        "start_progress": 0.831765935214211,
        "end_progress": 0.8772204806687566
    },
    {
        "text": "And she slipped a diamond into his hand.",
        "source": "user",
        "start_time": 522.0,
        "end_time": 549.0,
        "start_progress": 0.877742946708464,
        "end_progress": 0.8986415882967607
    },
    {
        "text": "\"You can keep this as a reward.\" And then she left.",
        "source": "user",
        "start_time": 549.0,
        "end_time": 565.0,
        "start_progress": 0.8991640543364682,
        "end_progress": 0.9258098223615465
    },
    {
        "text": "As I watched this on the screen I was so amazed.",
        "source": "user",
        "start_time": 565.0,
        "end_time": 583.0,
        "start_progress": 0.9263322884012539,
        "end_progress": 0.9524555903866249
    },
    {
        "text": "I guess in another life I finally learned that kindness can pay off in unexpected ways.",
        "source": "user",
        "start_time": 583.0,
        "end_time": 615.0,
        "start_progress": 0.9529780564263323,
        "end_progress": 0.9984326018808778
    }
]